                </p>

                <p>
                    My Product Design focused <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@menosketiago" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube channel</a>, is still far from reaching the minimum subscribers and watch time to enable monetization.
                </p>

                <p>
                    The <a href="https://figma.com/@menosketiago" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Figma community assets</a> I have published so far have been almost 100% free. The paid automation file that works with <a href="https://www.figma.com/community/file/1233490043546742002" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Style/token documentation componentsâ„¢</a> library has not made a single sale (it's a new product category so I expected as much).
