                        <p>
                            The assignment was to create a <b>React</b>-based modular component as part of a hypothetical Design System, and I felt like even if I did not get the job, I would spend a week improving my code chops. I wrapped the assignment, sent it in, and waited for the eventual thanks for doing it, but we are going forward with another candidate.
